entries.title: Escort the Engineers
entries.thanks_1: Nice flying out there. Those rebel fighters came out of no where. Almost like they were waiting for us.
entries.split_quest_alert: ALERT! Another Lamdba shuttle has been capture by rebel pilots. Proceed immediately to last know location and recover the shuttle.
entries.shields_depleted: We just lost our shields! We are not going to last much longer unless you can get those fighters off of us!
entries.hull_half: Pilot, we are under heavy fire down here! Get those fighters off of me.
entries.goodbye_1: Thanks for the escort, pilot. I wouldn't have made it without you.
entries.found_loc: Escort rendez-vous coordinates confirmed. Proceed as planned.
entries.failed_protect: What are you doing leaving me out here on my own? High Command will hear of your failure!
entries.failed_destroy: The Lambda shuttle has been destroyed. High Command will be most displeased with your performance. Report to your superior immediately.
entries.complete: Good work pilot. You have successfully protected the Empire's engineers so they can begin work on a most important project.
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.arrived_at_loc: Arrived at destination. Wait here for the engineers to disembark and shuttle to hyper jump.
entries.abort: High Command will hear about your failure in your duty, pilot.
